--------------------------------------------------------------------------
Build Steps
--------------------------------------------------------------------------

 % mkdir build
 % cd build
 % ../configure
 % make

to build for Linux ARM target (to run on zynq board), use

  ../configure --host=arm-xilinx-linux-gnueabi 

and make sure you have the Xilinx SDK in your PATH

e.g.

which arm-xilinx-linux-gnueabi-gcc
/opt/Xilinx/Vivado/2013.4/../../SDK/2013.4/gnu/arm/lin/bin/arm-xilinx-linux-gnueabi-gcc


